The last date of appointment of officers of the "Industry Officer (Technical) (Group-B)" cadre at the establishment of the Directorate of Industries under the Department of Industries, dated 01.01.2024 (dated 01.01.2023 to date 31.12.2023) has been published under reference number 3 above. Thereafter, the Directorate of Industries has submitted a proposal under reference 4 for publication of the provisional notification dated 01.01.2025 and in pursuance of this proposal, the provisional notification dated 01.01.2025 for the category "Industrial Officer (Technical) (Group-B)" is being published as Annexure-III annexed thereto.
